{
  "id": "adv_card_suz_14_01",
  "title": "成宮すず",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――琴乃のソロツアー、千秋楽",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "まさか琴乃のツアーですずが\nソロ曲を歌うことになるなんてな",
      "startTime": 4.8285714377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "引き受けてくれてありがとう\nでも初披露がここで本当に良かったのか？",
      "startTime": 10.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.7999999206
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "当然ですわ。むしろ、琴乃の提案には\n感謝していますのよ",
      "startTime": 17.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃のアンサーソングも私のこの曲も\nどちらも麻奈様に贈るものですから",
      "startTime": 24.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.1719954651
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "初披露するのにこれ以上の\nステージはありませんわ！",
      "startTime": 29.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "会場に来てくれるファンはもちろん……私達を見守って\nくれている麻奈様にも、喜んでいただけますわよね",
      "startTime": 36.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.0363716286
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "きっとな。二人の歌声は麻奈に届くと信じているよ\n琴乃の苦労も、すずの苦労も報われるさ",
      "startTime": 46.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃も大変だったとは聞いていたが……\nすずの方もかなり難航していたもんな",
      "startTime": 53.3333340962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.3363723915
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうですわね……でも{user}さんの\nおかげでなんとかなりましたわ",
      "startTime": 60.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "役に立ったのなら良かったよ。けど提案した時は\nあんなことになるなんて思いもしなかったけどな",
      "startTime": 67.7906987853,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――すずのソロ曲完成前",
      "startTime": 71.8503857137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 73.1170559408
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "ぐぬ、ぐぬぬぬ……わ、分かってはいましたが\n作詞作曲ってこんなにも難しいものでしたのね……",
      "startTime": 80.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "まさか歌詞すら思い浮かばないなんて\nあぁ、プロの方々を改めて尊敬しますわ……",
      "startTime": 90,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ゼロから作るとなると相当悩むよなぁ。俺も何か助けに\nなれたらいいんだが……テーマは決まっているのか？",
      "startTime": 100.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……具体的には何も……まずはこれを\n固めないとどうしようもないですわよね",
      "startTime": 111.0999961853,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "はっ、芽衣とよく行く駄菓子屋さんなんてどうかしら？\nよく食べるお菓子から連想して……",
      "startTime": 120.066662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "駄菓子麩菓子、ドーナツポテトチップス\n不思議放課後、気持ちメロメロミックス",
      "startTime": 126.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "すずらしい歌詞だな……\nでも、なんだ、その可愛いのはどうなんだろうか……？",
      "startTime": 133.5333287557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "違う気がしますわね……せっかくのソロ曲ですし\n私らしさというか私の気持ちというか、むぅぅぅ……",
      "startTime": 144.9333295186,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "ついに登場、期待のセンター\nやきもち焼かずに、焼き肉焼こう……なんですの、これ",
      "startTime": 154.9333295186,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "なんですのと言われても……なぁすず？\n一度休みでも取ってみたらどうだ？",
      "startTime": 165.2333295186,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ここのところ新曲にかかりきりだろ？\nどこかへ遊びに行って気分転換するのもありだと思うぞ",
      "startTime": 170.666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "どこかへ……そうですわ！\n私、行きたい所がありましたの！",
      "startTime": 179.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "今度、星見市で春祭りがあるでしょう？\nそこで行われるミニライブを観に行きたいですわ！",
      "startTime": 186.166662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "未来のライバル達の勇姿……\nきっと新曲作りのいい刺激になりますもの！",
      "startTime": 193.0333396912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "休暇も仕事に活かせるように、か\nその意識の高さはさすがトップアイドルだな",
      "startTime": 201.5000063579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "当然ですわ！　{user}さんも\n見習ってくれていいですわよ！",
      "startTime": 208.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ははは……なら、俺も同行して\n勉強させてもらおうかな",
      "startTime": 214.5000063579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "（すずがちゃんと息抜き出来るか）\n（少し心配だしな……）",
      "startTime": 219.1666730245,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3953.1862741000054,
          "startTime": 223.1198592986
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――春祭り当日",
      "startTime": 221.767119901,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00",
      "startTime": 223.0333473206
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00",
      "startTime": 223.0333473206
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "わぁぁぁ……！　見てくださいまし！\n屋台がたっくさんありますわよ！",
      "startTime": 227.7333518982,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00",
      "startTime": 231.1244170036
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-suz018.m4a",
      "text": "射的にくじ引きに……や、焼肉串！？\nそんなものも売っていますの！？",
      "startTime": 236.7333518982,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00",
      "startTime": 239.4387478676
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-suz019.m4a",
      "text": "他にもかき氷にわたあめに……リンゴ飴！\n素敵なものだらけで目移りしてしまいますわ～！",
      "startTime": 244.9666852315,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00",
      "startTime": 249.389178547
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "（すず、楽しそうにしてるな）\n（息抜き出来るかなんて、いらない心配だったみたいだ）",
      "startTime": 252.5333518982,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
