      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-suz020.m4a",
      "text": "もう、何してますの？　ミニライブまで\nまだ時間がありますし、一緒に屋台巡りをしますわよ！",
      "startTime": 259.9999954224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "はは、分かった分かった\nあんまり急いで転ぶなよ？",
      "startTime": 267.7666852315,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-suz021.m4a",
      "text": "む、子供扱いしないでくださいまし！\nって、あれ……？　今の言葉……",
      "startTime": 274.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうしたんだ？　急に立ち止まって\nまさか具合悪くなったんじゃ……",
      "startTime": 282.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00",
      "startTime": 284.846576008
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-suz022.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、全く同じことを前にお父様にも……\nそうですわ、あれは星見まつりの日",
      "startTime": 290.0667137146,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-suz023.m4a",
      "text": "私がアイドルを志すきっかけとなった\n麻奈様のステージを観た日でしたわ",
      "startTime": 297.7667137146,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
