      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00",
      "startTime": 300.8455780832
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈のステージを？　そうか\nすずもあの日、あの場所にいたのか",
      "startTime": 304.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00",
      "startTime": 307.3455780832
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-suz024.m4a",
      "text": "あの時は久しぶりにお父様とお母様とお出掛けして\nついはしゃいでしまって……懐かしいですわね",
      "startTime": 311.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったのか……なら、今日も\nあの日と同じくらいいい日になるといいな",
      "startTime": 320.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
